# Keep this directory under version control even though its heavy contents
# (acts_*.npy, labels_*.npy, manifest_*.json activation shards) are git-ignored
# and regenerated by data_real.extract_activations. A single ImageNet epoch of
# patch activations is ~600 GB, so these shards are NEVER committed — stream or
# subset instead. See ../RUN_AT_SCALE.md (Storage planning).
